<body>
    <h1>CAP for Capacity Management</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"8effd0a1f17a" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-CAP-48=
585=E2=80=93ImplementProcesstoEstimateFutureCapacityRequirements"><strong>C=
AP-48585 =E2=80=93 Implement Process to Estimate Future Capacity Requiremen=
ts</strong></h1>
<p class=3D"media-group"><img height=3D"250" style=3D"margin: 2px; border: =
1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: text-bottom;" src=
=3D"5be5af5f1f88fe0593b44a92218a322bd427800ef2a80c9eb36f852e3c9d209a" width=
=3D"250"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"4506f3261033" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-1.Objective"><=
strong>1. Objective</strong></h2>
<p local-id=3D"22cbc75edc2b">Establish a <strong>standardized, repeatable c=
apacity management process</strong> to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f0ab9b2c-9bf7-4eb0-a5ef-ea3380d5e9a9">
<li local-id=3D"74a50065-e5e0-4b4b-b9fb-bca95acf567f">
<p local-id=3D"2e29970f32f5">Estimate future infrastructure capacity requir=
ements</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"69f2cfa4-8f30-4767-bd31-0159c5259636">
<p local-id=3D"9ad3f98a0d08">Identify capacity-related risks proactively</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"e09b2d39-3c62-4f48-96ef-edef096d3f70">
<p local-id=3D"c00551147761">Enable GOCC to operate a <strong>predictive, r=
unbook-driven model</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ad32a14f-2b58-43fc-86f4-5659bc624719">
<p local-id=3D"a4fba3190acd">Support <strong>MMM L2 maturity</strong> and <=
strong>Lapu=E2=80=91Lapu operational readiness</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d180be4f-aab9-4056-bd61-f56ff5295555">
<h2 local-id=3D"4cfdf6e522dc" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-2.Scope"><stro=
ng>2. Scope</strong></h2>
<p local-id=3D"f7f82921af3d"><strong>In Scope</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5f33540d-dcf2-461e-88dc-436ec8a0ace5">
<li local-id=3D"b4f95941-dcf2-4413-8a39-e3767ffe4e00">
<p local-id=3D"dbd8b41957b5">All <strong>Gold applications (Phase 1)</stron=
g> =E2=86=92 expand to full estate (~65 apps)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef1ed2d1-4da5-4bfc-bdbd-973679f32f51">
<p local-id=3D"56c1c16777f0">Core components:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"339e9ba3-2115-4c98-830a-47e23fa3223e">
<li local-id=3D"27e3b4ae-3b76-4d3d-8c31-49cf3070be6f">
<p local-id=3D"bda47f95cef9">Compute (CPU / memory)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8bdb63a7-c315-4065-aac2-ba4cc0249550">
<p local-id=3D"5b4908217167">Storage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9b494d4-d1c2-4ef9-8806-bcf4b65429ac">
<p local-id=3D"ac34957c90bf">Database growth</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf35fb42-2910-42e0-a294-64dfae14076d">
<p local-id=3D"1360564ab5f0">Batch processing windows</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"05eff0708292"><strong>Out of Scope (Phase 1)</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ddc75389-c229-406a-ac7d-6503c60c74fd">
<li local-id=3D"a7357390-972e-4e58-b120-34670ccbdd3a">
<p local-id=3D"6218b75d3985">Deep workload re-architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83d17484-307b-409f-840b-06e0268cba19">
<p local-id=3D"cf0b6c132ee1">Advanced ML forecasting models</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c396bed4-60c1-492c-9e09-19ccdfa7704a">
<h2 local-id=3D"12f0dd6f430a" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-3.SuccessCrite=
ria"><strong>3. Success Criteria</strong></h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a62a6188-a8a2-4836-a86d-86a9267caa9b">
<li local-id=3D"c1771ca5-d3cb-47cc-961b-89b42f4bf119">
<p local-id=3D"26932ccd9295">100% of Gold applications have:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"89eeb8aa-0e15-42fa-b9ec-e67e79bbd26d">
<li local-id=3D"32094206-3b0d-4e20-9553-80db827f0711">
<p local-id=3D"59f7753e03b7">Baseline + 6=E2=80=9312 month capacity forecas=
t</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f6775d22-e52e-44d9-9852-ad0c626b3d35">
<p local-id=3D"6412dc4d7d74">Defined thresholds and trigger actions</p></li=
>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"5449d927-d0c5-4f0f-b56f-4c649f5d262b">
<p local-id=3D"4f2f13592be9">Capacity risk integrated into:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6c1c1cff-f29e-41d7-8cfa-91e8ebb1b5d1">
<li local-id=3D"d2625e04-573f-4afc-be78-e3bc3536996c">
<p local-id=3D"8c04757afbb2">RRP (Rapid Recovery Plan)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e0b330f-68f7-4729-a132-d94e0ee43826">
<p local-id=3D"0c8cbed3fe98">MMM L2 dashboards</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"40f5e276-082b-43a1-afb0-18a3fab26136">
<p local-id=3D"7842e250f506">GOCC owns ongoing monitoring + forecast update=
s</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8b7bcce3-a533-4d8c-ab18-e5c7e1b25efd">
<h2 local-id=3D"bc04d1eec0c3" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-4.OperatingMod=
elAlignment"><strong>4. Operating Model Alignment</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"ac=
5b67ed-8594-4ba3-ab3c-c185b3fb9681" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"735a3d41-4722-4114-a841-e763f1e552be">
<th data-local-id=3D"9dd4f5f9-8147-4332-97d3-96d6d403ba82" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"afaf0ca42496">Area</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"546085ce-2091-4042-98c9-523ddfbf6ab0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5b75d3da97df">Alignment</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f4d9caf0-50be-4efe-8c48-b3abe20444eb">
<th data-local-id=3D"39998698-f432-4ddf-a062-2cf08d60cc39" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"57f047eb2c58"><strong>Lapu=E2=80=91Lapu</strong></p></th>
<td data-local-id=3D"06008395-85f1-4ba4-8c0b-283ff3abd4d5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0069e2cacc88">Standardized, automatable, evidence-based outp=
uts</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fe9a38df-17eb-4778-b273-1ec2afc6cdd1">
<th data-local-id=3D"5f90d867-b3dd-4d35-9fd9-a4caf3717735" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0bbb8ec051f0"><strong>GOCC</strong></p></th>
<td data-local-id=3D"4f43a188-b06b-4ecf-88e7-26c2a99268bc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"85bb41d8a51f">Runbook-driven execution, centralized ownershi=
p</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"82551948-6c78-4967-ab64-a07757209ab4">
<th data-local-id=3D"e849ba4d-01be-4978-8d50-c7baceb71cfb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"13620e98ff83"><strong>MMM L2</strong></p></th>
<td data-local-id=3D"d504ceaa-cfca-461b-a4c5-b6e75914c168" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8dff70d03162">Predictive monitoring + risk-based thresholdin=
g</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9d694bf2-be38-43da-8cae-f502400ec4fa">
<th data-local-id=3D"0e82a4ab-cf41-4d9b-8cc8-12cb0fc4d54f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6c730ff2ac7f"><strong>RRP</strong></p></th>
<td data-local-id=3D"48a8c6bb-e7a4-47fa-8dce-4569f3cbee12" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"316fe9cdb8cb">Capacity risk scenarios included in recovery p=
lanning</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"0d1d82c3-9f4b-4e50-ac83-fe40991bebac">
<h2 local-id=3D"d3a1de776040" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-5.WorkPackages=
&amp;Deliverables"><strong>5. Work Packages &amp; Deliverables</strong></h2=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"1d31f4c0c555" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-WP1=E2=80=93Ca=
pacityBaselineEstablishment"><strong>WP1 =E2=80=93 Capacity Baseline Establ=
ishment</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"f2c399a8b4f3"><strong>Objective:</strong> Create auditable b=
aseline for all in-scope systems</p>
<p local-id=3D"6f94b2eb1794"><strong>Key Activities</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"24751ab9-c28f-40fe-9ef6-089aebe3e5ef">
<li local-id=3D"489d5fca-49fe-45c8-a010-e6b8e7ee1800">
<p local-id=3D"45db185dfcc2">Identify application =E2=86=92 CI mapping (CMD=
B alignment)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e14616c-ae59-4e57-9bec-82e748ec9d0d">
<p local-id=3D"ac8c71430990">Extract:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4c6909c0-1330-46aa-a45a-6e4871d49514">
<li local-id=3D"e8012783-d390-41da-9c6d-a83d74b50d39">
<p local-id=3D"a0479b418c04">Current utilization (CPU, memory, storage)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"194b5189-d118-4219-93ee-e566e0e15066">
<p local-id=3D"b47c8f71b4e0">Peak vs average load</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74371764-d0ce-4802-a495-837a442d5a2f">
<p local-id=3D"d8b4b95ec634">Historical trends (last 3=E2=80=936 months)</p=
></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"27cbaab2-73eb-46f7-9924-80e439414b5d">
<p local-id=3D"b5575222cbf4">Identify known capacity-related incidents</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7eedb0247354"><strong>Deliverables</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b9c56c25-309e-47fa-90c9-615f83d5bf31">
<li local-id=3D"debadefc-e7db-4277-8252-49aa0e44c9d6">
<p local-id=3D"831f1cb1b274"><strong>D1.1 Capacity Baseline Dataset (standa=
rd format)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ebd38de7-db21-4507-9f55-311054320dc0">
<p local-id=3D"e9050d6625ef"><strong>D1.2 Data Source Inventory (NR, logs, =
GOCC inputs)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94e9ed0e-3ca0-476d-a205-ac923d3bf546">
<p local-id=3D"2a63c1cbc52b"><strong>D1.3 Data Quality Assessment</strong><=
/p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3c0c2c8f22a1"><strong>Owner</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5c42a8cf-556e-4151-9dc2-558aed0f461d">
<li local-id=3D"a0ae1f18-6aa4-46cb-baa5-2e5e5affe7d6">
<p local-id=3D"2a8c2db4cb1e"><strong>Primary:</strong> GOCC</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c960da8b-2be1-4fb8-8a87-8d403362431c">
<p local-id=3D"aadc802cfca3"><strong>Support:</strong> Application Teams / =
ETS Monitoring</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6c570934-1c40-42d7-b384-0fa61e05710e">
<h3 local-id=3D"d72bd76ec6c4" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-WP2=E2=80=93De=
mandDriverDefinition"><strong>WP2 =E2=80=93 Demand Driver Definition</stron=
g></h3>
<p local-id=3D"ed4465c56939"><strong>Objective:</strong> Standardize how bu=
siness demand translates to capacity</p>
<p local-id=3D"d27e5a6979cb"><strong>Key Activities</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"dbd990ac-0d87-40df-ad44-4dabc06b6769">
<li local-id=3D"2b18f80c-14b2-4c3e-8e27-a66000576453">
<p local-id=3D"2fca296da45e">Define common driver categories:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"68a1a45d-ec46-488e-9bfa-f42dacc67e1a">
<li local-id=3D"5d8a4ef8-a4b7-42f4-a8dc-564ce8abb8ca">
<p local-id=3D"f58e7466b501">Transaction volume (e.g., Ingenium growth)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"091d39aa-169e-4eae-a638-5bcf512a4787">
<p local-id=3D"221b822f2e82">Batch volume / runtime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bcf50978-6853-4952-9345-a0d45c8f6c62">
<p local-id=3D"9c091061cbc1">User concurrency</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"92534b57-d4a3-41b5-b3b4-7c708b553acd">
<p local-id=3D"13ffc8477dea">Data growth</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2246635f-b097-4d47-8999-6eaa51ec7420">
<p local-id=3D"3c5c3d25cf40">Map drivers to each application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f92d08f-41af-47ec-bf34-ec0c59bbadff">
<p local-id=3D"16a756eb5dd9">Create simple driver-to-resource relationships=
</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8e3da604cd30"><strong>Deliverables</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac162743-2b66-4c12-895b-819098e5cef0">
<li local-id=3D"9b194640-6e2e-4ef2-875e-35fa0d8eb5a1">
<p local-id=3D"bf4b67fb8c77"><strong>D2.1 Standard Demand Driver Template</=
strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"075d3f9f-4fa6-44a9-8054-85298b810d46">
<p local-id=3D"fc7b29e37652"><strong>D2.2 Application Driver Mapping Matrix=
</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2777dc41f85a"><strong>Owner</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"85afeec1-9eab-435c-b7b9-c17814a3faa4">
<li local-id=3D"875f8d7e-b17e-48ce-bd1d-0cb078b7fe12">
<p local-id=3D"d019086e21db"><strong>Primary:</strong> ETS (you / central p=
rogram)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4d67505-d528-4f9f-bd60-7493a2e5a4a9">
<p local-id=3D"e067d7509994"><strong>Support:</strong> App Owners / Busines=
s SMEs</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"38985ec4-a646-402d-a648-954992125778">
<h3 local-id=3D"cafc37b2975f" id=3D"CAPforCapacityManagement-WP3=E2=80=93Fo=
recastingModel(StandardMethodology)"><strong>WP3 =E2=80=93 Forecasting Mode=
l (Standard Methodology)</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"4541dc336250"><strong>Objective:</strong> Establish a simple=
, auditable projection model</p>
<p local-id=3D"08d629b7bd83"><strong>Key Activities</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"eaf6066b-ed46-48c2-a839-23d672c199f7">
<li local-id=3D"82dca5a1-daf5-4626-b933-85d4de9eba34">
